What you need to know:

Just like they have been doing for the last few months, the athletes woke up and went to the stadium to continue with their preps only to be turned away from the facility by the contractors who are working on the siteA notice seen by Nation Sport at the entrance of the facility states that no sporting events will go on at the stadium until further noticeIn less than a month, the world will be converging in Chorzow, Poland for the World Relays and a number of Kenyan athletes are still struggling to qualify for the games due to lack of competitions